snippet.textDisplay: This was my favorite dungeon simply because of the somewhat unsettling atmosphere you feel when you walk through it...the eerie music creates that tone for when these are just old, dusty ruins, and even for this hi-tech stage. The premise was brilliant, the dungeon itself was enjoyable, and...this is my favorite Zelda game! (For now, maybe.)
